Titolo: Ultimate Custom Night

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Ultimate Custom Night (alternatively known as Five Nights at Freddy's 7) is a point-and-click survival horror video game created by Scott Cawthon. It is the seventh canon game in the Five Nights at Freddy's video game series, the eighth game overall, and is chronologically set after the events of the sixth game. The game was released on June 27, 2018 for free on Steam and Game Jolt. A mobile port for iOS and Android was released on April 28, 2020, with console ports released on April 30, 2021. The game was originally intended to be DLC for Freddy Fazbear's Pizzeria Simulator, but was later developed into its own separate game. A sequel, Five Nights at Freddy's: Help Wanted, was released on May 28, 2019.



Genere: Survival horror

Valutazione: N/A
